    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hey @rori4! So it looks like you specify the value of `fork` in your `truffle-config.js` under `networks.develop.fork`. That value gets passed to Ganache when it is initialized internally in Truffle. You can check out [the Ganache docs for options](https://www.npmjs.com/package/ganache-cli#options) and see how it works!\r\n\r\nIf that doesn't clear it up and you have more questions then feel free to ask!",
